                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18070218-21-off117 t18070218-21-cd118"></join>, eleven pound weight of brass, value 9 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18070218-21-victim288" type="victimName">
                     George 
                     Penton
                  <interp inst="t18070218-21-victim288" type="surname" value="Penton"></interp>
